meta.name: Sensor Showcase-Template
meta.description: template created from dashboard: Sensor Showcase

queries.text:
from(bucket: v.buckets)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == v.measurements)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "air_pressure")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 10s, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
